title: Two Whats?! And A Wow! - Larger Than Life
description:
Why is the huge ball of quinoa in Mindy's Gingerbread house? And what does that have to do with the World's Largest rubber duck and organism? We've got the questions AND the answers on today's gigantic round of Two Whats?! And A Wow! We're challenging you to separate the facts from the fiction about the largest things in the world!
